{"vv3:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv3:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv3:0.3":"Pithavagga ","vv3:0.4":"3. Tatiyapithavimanavatthu ","vv3:1.1":"“Pitham te sovannamayam ularam, ","vv3:1.2":"Manojavam gacchati yenakamam; ","vv3:1.3":"Alankate malyadhare suvatthe, ","vv3:1.4":"Obhasasi vijjurivabbhakutam. ","vv3:2.1":"Kena tetadiso vanno, ","vv3:2.2":"kena te idha mijjhati; ","vv3:2.3":"Uppajjanti ca te bhoga, ","vv3:2.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv3:3.1":"Pucchami tam devi mahanubhave, ","vv3:3.2":"Manussabhuta kimakasi punnam; ","vv3:3.3":"Kenasi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv3:3.4":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv3:4.1":"Sa devata attamana, ","vv3:4.2":"moggallanena pucchita; ","vv3:4.3":"Panham puttha viyakasi, ","vv3:4.4":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv3:5.1":"“Appassa kammassa phalam mamedam, ","vv3:5.2":"Yenamhi evam jalitanubhava; ","vv3:5.3":"Aham manussesu manussabhuta, ","vv3:5.4":"Purimaya jatiya manussaloke. ","vv3:6.1":"Addasam virajam bhikkhum, ","vv3:6.2":"vippasannamanavilam; ","vv3:6.3":"Tassa adasaham pitham, ","vv3:6.4":"pasanna sehi panibhi. ","vv3:7.1":"Tena metadiso vanno, ","vv3:7.2":"tena me idha mijjhati; ","vv3:7.3":"Uppajjanti ca me bhoga, ","vv3:7.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv3:8.1":"Akkhami te bhikkhu mahanubhava, ","vv3:8.2":"Manussabhuta yamakasi punnam; ","vv3:8.3":"Tenamhi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv3:8.4":"Vanno ca me sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv3:9.1":"Tatiyapithavimanam tatiyam. "}